  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Guest Relations Officer",
  "description": "<p>Job Responsibilities:<br /><br />1.\tServe customers and provide product information</p><p>2.\tAssist customers with seafood, vegetable, and bakery selections</p><p>3.\tWeigh, pack, label, and price products accurately</p><p>4.\tReplenish shelves and ensure proper product display</p><p>5.\tCheck product freshness and report any quality issues</p><p>6.\tMaintain cleanliness of shop floor, display areas, and equipment</p><p>7.\tAssist with receiving deliveries and stock arrangement</p><p>8.\tOperate POS system and handle cash or digital payments</p><p>9.\tFollow food hygiene and safety guidelines</p><p>10. Assist Supervisor to approach nearby business owners to promote company products</p><p>11. Assist in maintaining B2B membership records and documentation as required.</p><p>12.\tPerform other ad-hoc duties as assigned by Superior.<br /></p><p>Job Requirement:<br /></p><p>•\tWillingness to handle fresh seafood and food items</p><p>•\tFriendly attitude and good communication skills</p><p>•\tAble to stand for long hours and perform light lifting</p><p>•\tGood and understanding of B2B customer service</p><p>•\tAble to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays</p>",
